Rome Mayor Estimates Riot Damage at 1 Million Euros, Ansa Says

-- B y   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i
-- 
2011-10-16T11:16:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/rome-mayor-estimates-riot-damage-at-1-million-euros-ansa-says.html
Rome had at least 1 million euros
($1.39 million) in damages from rioting yesterday, Ansa newswire
reported, citing Mayor Giovanni Alemanno.  Damages included those to public transport and paving and
for cleaning work, Ansa reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
